      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoIs extracted from the CFD model must be directly mapped to the clinical hemolysis acceptance threshold with documented traceability at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) is the primary QoI and maps to the clinical threshold. However, secondary stress-exposure metrics used in the damage model are not independently validated. Achieved Gradation 3."
